Description: Pamir AI E-Ink Display Driver (DKMS)
 This package provides a DKMS (Dynamic Kernel Module Support) driver
 for Pamir AI E-Ink displays using the SSD1681 controller.
 .
 Features:
  - Support for 128x250 monochrome E-Ink displays
  - Multiple update modes (full, partial, base map)
  - Framebuffer interface (/dev/fb0)
  - Sysfs control interface
  - IOCTL control for advanced features
  - Deep sleep mode for power efficiency
 .
 Compatible with Raspberry Pi CM5 and other SPI-enabled devices.
